('Grubenteufel', 'Pit Fiend', 'Neun Höllen', 'rare', 'Einzelgänger', 'Jeder', 'Fleischfresser', 'Genial', 'Keins', 'LE', -5, '15, Fl 24', '13', 13.0, 7, '6', '1d4/1d4/1d6/2d6/2d4/1d4+2', 'Gift (SV-Tod), Furcht-Aura, Feuerball 1/Runde', '+3 Waffen nötig, Regeneration 2 HP/Runde', 50, 'L', 'Fanatic (18)', 18, 20000, 'melee', TRUE, '["detect magic","detect invisibility","fireball","hold person","improved invisibility","polymorph self","produce flame","pyrotechnics","wall of fire","meteor swarm (1/day)","symbol (1/day)"]'::jsonb, 'MM', 'Mächtigste der normalen Teufel — riesige geflügelte Schrecken die über Legionen der Hölle gebieten.'),
